NASAL PITCH 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Whoever stars in "The Nanny" (CBS) has the most horrendous-sounding voice I 
have ever heard.The audience was laughing, so I guess it was funny, but the 
irritating, loud voice was so nauseous sounding. I sure hope someone (at CBS) 
will ask her to tone it down a bit. 
</P>
<P>
 Barbara Talbert, Santa Clarita 
</P>
<P>
 Editor's Note: The voice belongs to Fran Drescher. 
