<P>
 THE SIERRA CLUB GUIDE TO 35mm LANDSCAPE PHOTOGRAPHY by Tim Fitzharris (Sierra 
Club: $18.; 110 pp., illustrated, paperback original). Nature photographer Tim 
Fitzharris presents clear instructions on how to take effective landscape 
photographs. He covers equipment, framing, cropping and the best time of day to 
shoot, as well as basic tips on using computer programs to combine images. This 
handsome book would make an excellent accompaniment to the holiday gift of a 
camera. 
</P>
