Boyz II Men (5) 4 8 Best Of, Sade (22) 5 9 Dookie, Green Day (7) 10 10 
Unplugged In New York, Nirvana (8) 6 TOP 10 SINGLES 03,04,39,11 Title, Artist 
(National Rank) Last Week 1 The Hotstepper, Ini Kamoze (1) 1 2 Tootsee Roll , 
69 Boyz (6) 2 3 On Bended Knee, Boyz II Men (3) 3 4 Creep, TLC (2) 4 5 Before I 
Let You Go, Blackstreet (8) 6 6 I Wanna Be Down, Brandy (7) 5 7 Playaz Club 
Remix, Rappin' 4-Tay (29) 7 8 Another Night, Real McCoy (4) 8 9 Short Dick Man, 
Twenty Fingers (9) 9 10 Secret, Madonna (13) 10 TOP 10 HARD ROCK ALBUMS 
