</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Ice Cube, "Bootlegs & B-Sides," (**) Street Knowledge/Priority. Did we really 
need a remix of Ice Cube's weakest single to date, "You Know How We Do It"? 
This lackluster, partly superfluous collection includes B-sides, remixes and 
three new songs, but only one of the new ones, the fiery "You Don't Wanna ---- 
With These," comes close to Cube at his best. 
</P>
<P>
 New albums are rated on a scale of one star (poor), two stars (fair), three 
stars (good) and four stars (excellent).  
</P>
