</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 In an effort to combat bias in mortgage lending in Los Angeles County, the 
Multi-Cultural Real Estate Alliance for Urban Change has set up a telephone 
hot-line to collect information on rejected home loan applications. 
</P>
<P>
 Real estate agents or borrowers who suspect discrimination in a loan 
transaction should call 213/299-5676 (HOT LINE). 
