county office in the commingled pool. As the Orange County financial debacle 
continues to unfold, it is uncertain what the ramifications will be to my 
district as well as 26 others that merely followed the law. It would appear 
that districts like mine, whose only risk was to follow the law, will be 
punished. The same state Legislature that makes the laws seems to be turning 
its back on the 27 law-abiding school districts. These districts were not 
