 Westminster 0, La Puente 0, (Westminster wins on penalty kicks 4-3) -- Leo 
Gimenez had the winning penalty kick for Westminster (4-2-2). The Lions will 
play Bellflower St. John Bosco today in the quarterfinals. In an earlier game, 
David Kurien had two goals for Westminster in a 5-0 victory over Monrovia.  
</P>
