 Tustin 2, Foothill 1 -- Doug Gonzalez scored the winning goal for Tustin 
(3-2-2). Jerry Gandorillas also scored for the Tillers off an assist from 
Gonzalez. Chris McCauley scored for Foothill. 
</P>
