 Mission Viejo 2, La Canada 1 -- Jill Erickson and Michelle De Liema scored for 
Mission Viejo (6-3-1). 
</P>
<P>
 In the Los Gatos girls' soccer tournament: 
</P>
<P>
 Mater Dei 3, Cupertino Homestead 0 -- Kim Buccola, Michelle Perez and Katie 
Ticehurst each scored for Mater Dei (3-3-2), which will play Danville San Ramon 
Monday. In an earlier game, Mater Dei lost, 4-0, to San Jose Presentation. 
</P>
<P>
 In nonleague girls' soccer: 
</P>
<P>
 Santa Margarita 2, Encinitas San Dieguito 1 -- Kristen Rowe and Suzie Mora 
each scored to lead visiting Santa Margarita (2-1-1). Amy Nesbitt had four 
saves for the Eagles. 
</P>
