<P>
 Sergio Hernandez and Chad Fister, who scored 13 and 11 points, were named to 
the all-tournament team for Sonora. 
</P>
<P>
 Sonora, which improved to 7-2, played as the visitor on its home floor and 
opened an eight-point lead to end the first quarter. 
</P>
